44:23.870 --> 44:26.790
You have a favorite. [laughing]

44:26.873 --> 44:28.041
I love this foot.

44:28.124 --> 44:30.293
- Mwah.
- Oh, you are so weird.

44:30.377 --> 44:31.795
Do that again.

44:31.878 --> 44:34.506
- Yes, ma'am.
- [laughing]

