Well, what are
you asking me for?

45:14.462 --> 45:16.381
You're the one
always inviting me for rides.

45:16.464 --> 45:17.382
- Let's go.
- No.

45:17.465 --> 45:18.800
Not with me.

45:18.883 --> 45:20.802
Well, come on.
We'll-we'll see what happens.

45:20.885 --> 45:22.554
- Hit the gas.
- Okay! Okay!

45:22.637 --> 45:23.972
- Brace yourself.
- Good.

45:24.055 --> 45:25.223
- [laughing]
- [chuckles]

45:25.306 --> 45:27.225
Woo-hoo!

45:27.308 --> 45:28.852
- [laughing]
- Yippee!

45:28.935 --> 45:30.353
This is fun.

45:30.437 --> 45:31.938
- Right?
- [grinding]

45:32.021 --> 45:33.773
Uh-oh.

45:35.024 --> 45:36.943
Okay, well...

45:37.026 --> 45:38.611
Here we go. Manual mode.

45:38.695 --> 45:40.238
[chuckling]

45:41.656 --> 45:43.575
[chuckling]

45:47.996 --> 45:49.414
[chuckles softly]

45:50.832 --> 45:52.250
[exhales]

45:52.333 --> 45:54.002
Been a while since we've done
that, hasn't it?

45:54.085 --> 45:56.004
[chuckling]

45:58.923 --> 46:00.925
[crickets chirping in distance]

46:03.428 --> 46:05.346
You hear that?

46:06.681 --> 46:08.516
No. What?

46:11.060 --> 46:12.937
Well, they're playing our song.

46:13.021 --> 46:14.606
[chuckles]

46:16.566 --> 46:18.985
♪ Hold me close ♪

46:19.068 --> 46:20.904
♪ Hold me tight ♪

46:22.030 --> 46:24.282
♪ Make me thrill ♪

46:24.365 --> 46:26.201
♪ With delight ♪

46:27.994 --> 46:31.915
♪ Let me know where I stand ♪

46:31.998 --> 46:34.209
♪ From the start ♪

